@startuml HighLevelSequence
title High-Level Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant UI
participant Logic
participant Model
participant Storage

User -> UI: Enter command
activate UI

UI -> Logic: execute(commandText)
activate Logic

Logic -> Model: parse + execute command\n(read/update in-memory data)
activate Model
Model --> Logic: Command result / updated state
deactivate Model

Logic -> Storage: saveAddressBook(model data)
activate Storage
Storage --> Logic: save success
deactivate Storage

Logic --> UI: CommandResult
deactivate Logic

UI --> User: Show feedback + refreshed list
deactivate UI
@enduml
